    <item>
      <title>加拿大扩大空中边境监视以安抚特朗普</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/canada-expands-aerial-border-surveillance-to-pacify-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大正在部署所谓的“空中情报工作组”，这是新一轮 13 亿加元（9.08 亿美元）计划的一部分，旨在解决美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普对移民和芬太尼穿越北部边境的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/canada-expands-aerial-border-surveillance-to-pacify-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 21:03:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Ardonagh 凭借 Stone Point 的投资实现 140 亿美元估值</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/ardonagh-said-to-have-14-billion-value-with-stone-point-stake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，英国保险经纪公司 Ardonagh Group 已获得 Stone Point Capital 的新投资，这使得这家英国保险经纪公司的估值在三年内几乎翻了一番，达到 140 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/ardonagh-said-to-have-14-billion-value-with-stone-point-stake</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 19:48:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
